<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" href="favicon.png"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="w3.css"/>
    <title>Treinos</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="w3-sidebar w3-animate-left w3-pale-green w3-border w3-bar-block" style="width:25%">
        <h3 class="w3-bar-item w3-pale-green">Páginas Disponíveis</h3>
        <% for (const page of pageList) { %>
            <a href="<%= page.url %>" class="w3-bar-item w3-button w3-border-bottom"><%= page.name %></a>
        <% } %>
    </div>
      
    <div style="margin-left:25%">
        <h1 class="w3-card w3-teal w3-border">Treinos</h1>

        <p>Esta página web tem como principal objetivo testar formulários HTML e as suas aplicações.</p>
        <p>(CRUD) - Insert, Delete, Update, Retrive</p>
        
        <footer class="w3-container w3-teal" style="text-align: right;">
            <p>Author: <%= author %> &copy; </p>
            <p>Date: <%= date %> </p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>